+Name:           lua51-luafilesystem
+Version:        1.8.0
+Release:        0
+Summary:        File System Library for the Lua Programming Language
+License:        MIT
+URL:            https://github.com/lunarmodules/luafilesystem
+Source0:        https://github.com/lunarmodules/luafilesystem/archive/refs/tags/v1_8_0.tar.gz
+BuildRequires:  gcc
+BuildRequires:  lua51-devel
+BuildRequires:  make
+
+%description
+LuaFileSystem is a Lua library developed to complement the set of
+functions related to file systems offered by the standard Lua distribution.
+LuaFileSystem offers a portable way to access the underlying directory
+structure and file attributes.
+
+%prep
+%autosetup -p1 -n luafilesystem-%{version}
+
+%build
+make LUA_VERSION=%{lua_version}
+
+%install
+mkdir -p %{buildroot}%{lua_archdir}
+make install DESTDIR=%{buildroot} PREFIX=/usr LUA_LIBDIR=%{buildroot}%{lua_archdir}
+
+%files
+%license LICENSE
+%doc README.md
+%{lua_archdir}/lfs.so
+
+%changelog
